Class User

java.lang.Object
com.ttc.fitPT.ptSchedule.model.User
public class User extends Object
Represents a User in the system, including personal details, role information, and associated certifications.

      Constructs a new User object with basic details.

      personId - the unique identifier for the user.

      lastName - the last name of the user.

      lastName - the last name of the user.
      roleType - the role type of the user (e.g., ADMINISTRATOR, THERAPIST).
      roleId - the unique identifier for the user's role.
      email - the user's email address.
      phone - the user's phone number.
      username - the username of the user.
      password - the password of the user.
